PRUDENTIAL RIDELONDON - 3 AND 4 AUGUST 2019
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    Prudential RideLondon 2019 events will take place in central London
    on Saturday 3 August 2019 and in London and Surrey on Sunday 4
    August 2019.

    Some local road closures are planned on Sunday 4 August. The event
    on Saturday affects Central London only.

